---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Me">
  <section id="about" class="py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-12 text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
        <span class="text-primary">&lt;</span>
        About Me
        <span class="text-primary">/&gt;</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto" data-aos="fade-up">
        <p class="text-lg mb-6 text-light/80">
          I completed my studies at the <span class="gradient-text">University of Granada (UGR)</span>, earning a dual degree in <span class="gradient-text">Computer Engineering</span> and <span class="gradient-text">Business Administration</span>. Currently, I'm pursuing a Master's in <span class="gradient-text">Data Science and Computer Engineering</span>, specializing in <span class="gradient-text">Data Science and Intelligent Technologies</span>, while working professionally in the field.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6 text-light/80">
          I gained valuable hands-on experience during my internship as a <span class="gradient-text">Data Engineer</span>, where I worked on data pipelines, ETL processes, and data infrastructure. This experience solidified my passion for working with data and understanding how to transform raw information into actionable insights.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6 text-light/80">
          Currently, I work as an <span class="gradient-text">AI Engineer Junior</span> at <span class="gradient-text">NTT DATA</span>, where I focus on developing <span class="gradient-text">AI-powered solutions</span>, building <span class="gradient-text">intelligent automation systems</span>, and creating <span class="gradient-text">AI agents</span> that streamline business processes. My role allows me to explore cutting-edge technologies in the <span class="gradient-text">Artificial Intelligence</span> domain, combining my technical skills with innovative problem-solving.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6 text-light/80">
          I am deeply passionate about <span class="gradient-text">Artificial Intelligence</span> and its potential to transform industries. From machine learning models to generative AI and intelligent automation, I'm constantly exploring new ways to leverage AI technologies to create efficient, scalable, and impactful solutions. My goal is to continue growing in this exciting field, pushing the boundaries of what's possible with AI.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
    .gradient-text {
      background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff4b2b, #ff8c00, #ff4b2b); /* Rojo a naranja */
      background-size: 200% 200%;
      background-position: 0 0;
      color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      animation: gradient-animation 3s ease infinite;
    }
  
    @keyframes gradient-animation {
      0% {
        background-position: 0 0;
      }
      50% {
        background-position: 100% 100%;
      }
      100% {
        background-position: 0 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
  